然後押後裁決，繼續無了期關押肥佬黎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T18:55:49.000Z","msg":"天琦嘅刑期覆核都等咗差不多大半年先有結果"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T20:11:14.000Z","msg":"應該又係咁玩，拖到咁上下等上面order埋尾<br />\n贏輸都還押你一段時間先<br />\n<br />\n其實又係打壓嘅一種<br />\n告得入就睇中唔中quota 紅官鳩判<br />\n告唔入就玩唔可以保釋/還押<br />\n配合濫捕+599g真係咩人都任佢玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5539bf6cabf53232f677481793adca2af45f952","tid":2390711,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91057bdd841199a914df83daa693c0fc9a7633c3","tid":2390711,"uid":17721,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"98dbd33465ca41226df695fd988563799c5eb7b9","tid":2390711,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T18:06:19.000Z","msg":"周天行<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/GYlJmrgqyReuVWQTOQRyppj7UD0=/802x1301/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YHXMZXVRIZB4NJOZJI2F2O27RA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FGYlJmrgqyReuVWQTOQRyppj7UD0%3D%2F802x1301%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYHXMZXVRIZB4NJOZJI2F2O27RA.jpg&h=4f3e7ced&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T19:08:14.000Z","msg":"希望佢有一日自食其果"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T21:18:24.000Z","msg":"呢D人高速移民去英美澳加啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a23798d678e73a1204f1df0b5c11ab8f662672aa","tid":2390711,"uid":364767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T21:23:15.000Z","msg":"理由好簡單，律政司是為共產黨做事<br />\n鄭若驊已經脫離『司法公正』的軌道"},{"pid":"c76523e5c4fd9db65ea4960797aeb7a518bc6fb9","tid":2390711,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d04c1d1ad7be418fd0e611d0925c8acf3ab2c8a","tid":2390711,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T17:47:10.000Z","msg":"終審法院周一（1日）開庭審理壹傳媒創辦人黎智英涉違國安法一案，處理國安法第42(2)條下保釋的詮釋及門檻。律政司一方多次講述國安法是全國人大決定訂立的背景，法庭要在此前提理解及詮釋法例。雖然《基本法》第23條未正式立法，律政司署理副刑事檢控專員周天行庭上卻稱，法庭考慮批出保釋時，要考慮被告會否干犯未立法但危害國家安全的「行為」，例如《基本法》第23條禁止香港政治組織與外國政治組織或團體建立聯繫。終院開庭審理一天之後，宣佈押後裁決，黎智英須繼續還押監房。<br />\n<br />\n終審法院多名法官連番質疑律政司一方的說法，非常任法官陳兆愷質疑《基本法》23條下的罪行未立法，為什麼法庭要考慮？首席法官張舉能也質疑，街上所有人都可合法地做的行為，但被控違反國安法的被告卻因此被拒絕保釋，「這不是幾奇怪嗎？當所有人都可以做，點會幫助維護國家安全？」<br />\n<br />\n對於周天行質疑，根據國安法字眼，不論法庭對被告保釋條件嚴苛與否，對國安法下批出保釋無關。法官質疑，雖然律政司說國安法第42(2)條並非無保釋，但律政司對條文的理解，尤其法官只能根據字面理解、不考慮施加保釋條款，國安法下近乎完全不能批出保釋。<br />\n<br />\n非常任法官司徒敬直言不能理解律政司的說法，常任法官霍兆剛形容，法庭要平衡被告可能會干犯或不干犯違反國安法行為，質疑究竟點解（why on earth）法官不能考慮施加保釋條款？另一名常任法官李義甚至形容律政司說法「極端」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/37682/%E9%BB%8E%E6%99%BA%E8%8B%B1-%E6%B8%AF%E7%89%88%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95-%E7%B5%82%E5%AF%A9%E6%B3%95%E9%99%A2-37739/%E3%80%90%E9%BB%8E%E6%99%BA%E8%8B%B1%E6%A1%88%E3%80%91%E5%BE%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%8F%B8%E5%8A%9B%E9%8A%B7%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E6%80%A7-23%E6%A2%9D%E6%9C%AA%E7%AB%8B%E5%B7%B2%E9%81%A9%E7%94%A8-%E7%B5%82%E9%99%A2%E3%80%8C%E5%9C%8D%E6%94%BB%E3%80%8D%E5%BE%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%8F%B8%E6%BC%94%E7%B9%B9%E7%AD%89%E5%90%8C%E7%84%A1%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F37682%2F%25E9%25BB%258E%25E6%2599%25BA%25E8%258B%25B1-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%2589%2588%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E7%25B5%2582%25E5%25AF%25A9%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%2599%25A2-37739%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%25BB%258E%25E6%2599%25BA%25E8%258B%25B1%25E6%25A1%2588%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%25BE%258B%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%258F%25B8%25E5%258A%259B%25E9%258A%25B7%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%2587%258D%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%2580%25A7-23%25E6%25A2%259D%25E6%259C%25AA%25E7%25AB%258B%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E9%2581%25A9%25E7%2594%25A8-%25E7%25B5%2582%25E9%2599%25A2%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%259C%258D%25E6%2594%25BB%25E3%2580%258D%25E5%25BE%258B%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25BC%2594%25E7%25B9%25B9%25E7%25AD%2589%25E5%2590%258C%25E7%2584%25A1%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B&d=FyOxfEvlGqeE3CGJWKQQl5Mi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=448dabe0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/37682/%E9%BB%8E%E6%99%BA%E8%8B%B1-%E6%B8%AF%E7%89%88%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95-%E7%B5%82%E5%AF%A9%E6%B3%95%E9%99%A2-37739/%E3%80%90%E9%BB%8E%E6%99%BA%E8%8B%B1%E6%A1%88%E3%80%91%E5%BE%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%8F%B8%E5%8A%9B%E9%8A%B7%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E6%80%A7-23%E6%A2%9D%E6%9C%AA%E7%AB%8B%E5%B7%B2%E9%81%A9%E7%94%A8-%E7%B5%82%E9%99%A2%E3%80%8C%E5%9C%8D%E6%94%BB%E3%80%8D%E5%BE%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%8F%B8%E6%BC%94%E7%B9%B9%E7%AD%89%E5%90%8C%E7%84%A1%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T23:46:03.000Z","msg":"all are vase"},{"pid":"2d531bc8234b202f3a596ef3dc701b78bae239fe","tid":2390711,"uid":68111,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c45e79566c57e455acce358126f059acb6cfcd38","tid":2390711,"uid":31215,"like":1,"dislike":21,"score":-20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T17:59:13.000Z","msg":"睇黎有機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講返人話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />靠專業拎返司法先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T23:57:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />做完大戲 押後宣判 都囚多你一年半載"},{"pid":"97a904e490a23147316649852c1083157feb23aa","tid":2390711,"uid":37,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T23:59:39.000Z","msg":"仲係度同佢咬文嚼字根本戇鳩"},{"pid":"4cb9d2a8ff37b5b7a2b9858026e67b410cbeac70","tid":2390711,"uid":122915,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a729d9ea13090b228cdc655303174494505e532c","tid":2390711,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T17:50:38.000Z","msg":"黃繼明則說，辯方立場是法庭根本無需處理憲制性問題，認為只收窄至處理到底高等法院周家明及李運騰在唐英傑案中，到底是控方或辯方有舉證責任證明被告可獲保釋。黃狀說，如果高等法院兩名法官做法正確，則黎智英已勝出本案，無需處理憲制性問題。<br />\n<br />\n黃指出，根據普通法的預設立場，是應該推定批出保釋，即使條文寫法稍稍傾向預設不批證據，應該由控方提出證據證明。同時，他促請法庭考慮無罪推定原則及《公民權利和政治權利公約》等人權保障，國安法42(2)條的預設立場應是批出保障。<br />\n<br />\n不過，常任法官李官質疑根據國安法的字面理解，無論舉證責任誰屬，難以將預設立場說成是會批出保釋。<br />\n<br />\n首席法官張舉能也質疑，高院在唐英傑案中將國安法保釋與普通刑事法無分別，可能變相改寫國安法第42(2)條。<br />\n<br />\n黃繼明回應說，高院在唐英傑案中，已留意到國安法42(2)可能不同一般保釋，認為法庭不應猜度或過分解讀原審法官的意思。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T00:06:34.000Z","msg":"臨尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞咁大場龍鳳即係公開叫律政司又教佢地審案<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e701d7b4957226cdcd04db84ad9465a5e364856","tid":2390711,"uid":331421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T00:15:27.000Z","msg":"改基本法，將國安法終審權交畀最高人民法院咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f8206d185145c83da5a1ced69db91e8d7b03989","tid":2390711,"uid":114275,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T00:18:03.000Z","msg":"完全演繹出支那式法治同普世式法治嘅衝突<br />\n<br />\n雖然結果都係支那贏兩次"},{"pid":"2df161a960c9aacc22d90c6ebaeaa794563b434c","tid":2390711,"uid":6058,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T00:18:36.000Z","msg":"傻鳩發官話司法獨立<br />\n點知俾劣正屍當狗咁撚當曱甴咁踩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n繼續鳩噏司法獨立啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"557a4b2af1a1a9fda705f6b16a345a18ce50e973","tid":2390711,"uid":55011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T00:19:22.000Z","msg":"有哂script扮討論<img src=\"/